airplane?
W: No. We’ll get there by ship from 
Ulleungdo.
M: How exciting! Do you know how much it 
costs for the trip?
W: A tour package for two nights and three 
days is about $200 including 
accommodation. 
M: I think the price is reasonable. And... is it 
possible to drop by Gyeongju on the way 
back? I was told Gyeongju is a beautiful 
city.
W: Sure. Actually, it’s included in our trip.
M: Awesome! So we’re going there on the 
last day of July, right? I need to 
reschedule my part­time job.
W: Right. Make sure you don’t mess up the 
dates.
